# id: FakeKinesisBehavioursFactory -> NonReshardedStreamsKinesis -> private static boolean isValidShardId(String shardId)
commentText: Checks if a shard id has valid format._Kinesis stream shard ids have 12-digit numbers left-padded with 0's,_prefixed with "shardId-", ex. "shardId-000000000015".__@param shardId the shard id to check_@return whether the shard id is valid
codeText: private static boolean isValidShardId(String shardId) {_			if (shardId == null) {_				return false__			}_			return shardId.matches("^shardId-\\d{12}")__		}
